    • addContentToTheMapFile

      public void addContentToTheMapFile() throws InvalidInputException, EntityNotFoundException
      This test will add content to Continent List, Country List and Neighbour List.
      Throws:
      InvalidInputException - Any invalid input other than the reqired parameters will throw this error.
      EntityNotFoundException - Any Continent that is not found in the Continent List but added in the Country List will throw this error.

    • testSaveFile

      public void testSaveFile() throws ResourceNotFoundException, InvalidInputException, java.io.IOException
      This test will save the content added in Continent, Country and Neighbour List into the .map file.
      Throws:
      ResourceNotFoundException - Throws if the Target File where content is to be saved is not found then this exception will be raised.
      InvalidInputException - Throws if input is invalid.
      java.io.IOException - Throws if IOException is generated.
